**CORELATED SUBQUERY***
=====================
Q1)WAQ TO FIND OUT THE 3RD HIGHEST SALARY EMPLOYEES DETAILS?
ANS:=
SQL> SELECT * FROM EMP E1 WHERE 2=(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT SAL)FROM EMP E2 WHERE E2.SAL>E1.SAL);

     EMPNO ENAME      JOB              MGR HIREDATE         SAL       COMM
---------- ---------- --------- ---------- --------- ---------- ----------
    DEPTNO
----------
      7566 JONES      MANAGER         7839 02-APR-81       2975
        20
==================================================================================================
Q2)WAQ TO FIND OUT THE FIRST LOWEST SALARY EMPLOYEES DEATAILS?
ANS:=
SQL> SELECT * FROM EMP E1 WHERE 0=(SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT SAL)FROM EMP E2 WHERE E2.SAL<E1.SAL);

     EMPNO ENAME      JOB              MGR HIREDATE         SAL       COMM
---------- ---------- --------- ---------- --------- ---------- ----------
    DEPTNO
----------
      7369 SMITH      CLERK           7902 17-DEC-80        800
        20
==================================================================================================
Q3)WAQ TO DISPLAY IN TOP 3 HIGHEST SALARIES EMPLOYEES DETAILS
ANS:=
