***EXISTS OPERATOR*
Q5)WAQ TO DISPLAY DEPARTMENTS IN WHICH DEPARTMENTS THE EMPLOYEE ARE WORKING (EXISTING)? 
ANS=
SQL> SELECT DNAME FROM DEPT D WHERE EXISTS(SELECT DEPTNO FROM EMP E WHERE E.DEPTNO=D.DEPTNO);

DNAME
--------------
RESEARCH
SALES
ACCOUNTING
=====================================================================================Q6)WAQ TO DISPLAY DEPARTMENTS IN WHICH DEPARTMENTS THE EMPLOYEE ARE  NOT WORKING ( NOT EXISTING)?
ANS:=
SQL> SELECT DNAME FROM DEPT D WHERE NOT EXISTS(SELECT DEPTNO FROM EMP E WHERE E.DEPTNO=D.DEPTNO);

DNAME
--------------
OPERATIONS
================================================================================
Q7)WAQ TO DISPLAY EMPLOYEES WHO HAVE DEPARTMENT FROM EMP DEPARTMENTS TABLE?
ANS:=
SQL> SELECT ENAME FROM EMP E WHERE EXISTS(SELECT DEPTNO FROM DEPT D WHERE D.DEPTNO=E.DEPTNO);

