Q8)WAQ TO DISPLAY EMPLOYEES WHO ARE EXISTING UNDER ACCOUNTING,SALES DEPARTMENTS? 
ANS:=
SQL> SELECT ENAME,DEPTNO FROM EMP  E WHERE EXISTS(SELECT DEPTNO FROM DEPT D WHERE D.DEPTNO=E.DEPTNO AND DNAME IN('ACCOUNTING','SALES'));

ENAME          DEPTNO
---------- ----------
CLARK              10
KING               10
MILLER             10
ALLEN              30
WARD               30
MARTIN             30
BLAKE              30
TURNER             30
JAMES              30

=======================================================================
Q9)WAQ TO DISPLAY EMPLOYEES WHO ARE NOT EXISTING UNDER ACCOUNTING,SALES DEPARTMENTS?
ANS:=
SQL> SELECT ENAME,DEPTNO FROM EMP  E WHERE NOT EXISTS(SELECT DEPTNO FROM DEPT D WHERE D.DEPTNO=E.DEPTNO AND DNAME IN('ACCOUNTING','SALES'));

ENAME          DEPTNO
---------- ----------
SMITH              20
JONES              20
SCOTT              20
ADAMS              20
FORD               20

========================================================================
